  "original_title": "It\u2019s not lockdown, but working from home until July 10: Harin",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "It\u2019s not lockdown, but working from home until July 10: Harin",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Tourism Minister Harin Fernando said this is not a lockdown situation but it's working from home until July 10.",
        "He made this comment after the government has announced to issue fuel only for essential services from midnight today until July 10.",
        "\u201cDon\u2019t treat this as a lockdown situation, it's the work from home process until July 10 and hoping country will return to normalcy after that,\u201d he said.",
        "He also said that all other areas should function as they used to like other days.",
        "\u201cShops, pharmacies supermarkets etc. should function as normal days,\" he said."
      ],
